Author: obizcoin
Title: [ANN]SOFTCAP‚≠ê Obizcoin üöÄIntroducing AI and Blockchain backed Smart Process BOTs
Body: Hello Akentev, thank you so much for asking this questions. It gives us a chance to clarify things for you as well as many other potential investors having similar doubts.  No. OBIZCOIN does not plan to replace human CEO's. What OBIZCOIN is aiming is to make the life of a CEO easier.  How ?  OBIZCOIN is developing a Smart Business Process Automation BOT based on Artificial Intelligence and Blockchain technology. In startups and SME‚Äôs, because of limited resources, multiple job profiles are handled by those involved in the top management. They have to overlook all the processes of the organization like Sales, BD, Purchase, Logistics, HR, Accounts and so on. Handling too many things at the same time makes it difficult for them to achieve excellence in any business process. They are left with no time for evaluation or monitoring of the actual performances. Also lack of domain expertise lead them to take wrong decisions jeopardising their venture‚Äôs survival in the long run. This is where OBIZCOIN comes in picture.   OBIZCOIN Smart BOT will act as a virtual CEO for these Startups and SME‚Äôs helping them with domain expert knowledge, designing of efficient business processes, aligning their team to the designed processes, allocating automated tasks based on their KRA‚Äôs developed on the BOT system, monitoring team‚Äôs performances and rewarding them, training them as per performance results.  One of the core services of OBIZCOIN is ‚ÄúOperational Risk Score Analysis‚Äù. Often, while making any sort of business decisions, the only data available about that organization is the financial data. With the development of OBIZCOIN by next year, business owners and investors will have the access to an organization‚Äôs real time operational health which will help them analyse their businesses better and take corrective actions to improvise their business processes. Investors can have a better understanding of the real time operational health of the businesses they wish to invest in along with financial evaluation.   OBIZCOIN BOT Application will have API‚Äôs to connect with various software used by Organization to fetch data and make it usable. This will make users like the application because of its flexibility in blending with the existing business applications.  In addition to this, organization can have a  Operational Risk Score Analysis done to understand how strong their business processes are and know their organization‚Äôs operational health.  BOT will be a decentralized platform allowing other business consultants to develop their processes and use them for their clients. Thus it is an auto scalable model with multiple utility.  I hope this solves your query. Please let us know if you still have any doubts.
